@deffn {Function} objc-cffi:add-objc-class class-name super-class &optional ivar-list
@findex objc-cffi:add-objc-class
Adds and returns a new Objective @code{c} class `CLASS-NAME` deriving from `SUPER-CLASS`.

`IVAR-LIST` is a list of instance variable object that will be
added to the new class.

If a class with the same name already exists the method raise an
error of type @code{objc-class-already-exists}.
@end deffn
